Package org.pepstock.charba.client.annotation

Interface IsDefaultsAbstractPointedAnnotation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IsDefaultsAnnotation, IsDefaultsBackgroundColorHandler, IsDefaultsBorderOptionsHandler, IsDefaultsEventsHandler, IsDefaultsExtendedShadowOptionsHandler, IsDefaultsShadowOptionsHandler
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IsDefaultsAbstractCircleBasedAnnotation, IsDefaultsLabelAnnotation, IsDefaultsPointAnnotation, IsDefaultsPolygonAnnotation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCircleBasedAnnotation, AbstractPointedAnnotation, DefaultLabel, DefaultPoint, DefaultPolygon, LabelAnnotation, PointAnnotation, PolygonAnnotation
    interface IsDefaultsAbstractPointedAnnotation
extends IsDefaultsAnnotation, IsDefaultsBackgroundColorHandler, IsDefaultsExtendedShadowOptionsHandler
    This is the AnnotationPlugin.ID plugin annotation DEFAULTS options interface for annotation which are configured by a point in a chart.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
